 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="27ce21c" class="language- ">
 &lt;code>Set the English language and not French to have more verbose output during future problems.&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="keyboard">Keyboard &lt;a href="#keyboard" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>


 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

